    "name": "Broken World: Save Your Children",
    "steam_appid": 3312730,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312730/extras/789dd1adedc48b13bf39eedeb911fa34.poster.avif?t=1750305393\" width=800 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312730/extras/789dd1adedc48b13bf39eedeb911fa34.webm?t=1750305393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312730/extras/789dd1adedc48b13bf39eedeb911fa34.mp4?t=1750305393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 破碎世界：拯救你的孩子 中，是一款生存游戏，玩家扮演父亲 Josh，试图在僵尸末日中保护自己的孩子 Edrik 和 Emma 存活。你的目标是穿越一座废墟城市，到达机场，与等待你的妻子汇合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理口渴、饥饿和幸福感。建造武器、陷阱和掩体。探索、钓鱼、烹饪并战斗以求生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一个决定都至关重要。你会冒险获取补给还是选择安全路线？你会教孩子自立还是保护他们每一步？在破碎的世界中，父亲的爱是你最强大的武器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312730/extras/99fee4024b62daff4ae0c5ed8c8be921.avif?t=1750305393\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312730/extras_big/99fee4024b62daff4ae0c5ed8c8be921.avif?t=1750305393 width=800 height=532 /></span></p>",
